description.en:
TetoInu is an ERC-20 token named after the fox-squirrel character Teto from popular anime Nausicaa.

The token features a reflection mechanic that provides 2% returns on transactions for traders.

Total token supply is 1 quadrillion, total tax per transaction (buy & sell) is 10%.

The project team intends TetoInu to be the principal token in an eventual ecosystem including NFTs and a P2E game.
